# GeoTIFF Input Directory

This directory is where you organize your GeoTIFF files by type.

## Usage:
1. Create subfolders for each raster type (e.g., ambient/, shadows/, texture/, elevation/)
2. Place related GeoTIFF files (.tif/.tiff) in the appropriate folders
3. Run the processing scripts to generate tiles

## Example structure:
```
geotiff_input/
├── ambient/
│   ├── region1_ambient.tif
│   └── region2_ambient.tif
├── shadows/
│   └── shadows_data.tif
└── elevation/
    ├── dem_north.tif
    └── dem_south.tif
```

Each folder will be processed into a single tile pyramid using VRT technology.